## Estados validos

### Inception

| Campo | Valores |
|-------|---------|
| `inception.status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `completed` |
| `inception.approved` | `true`, `false` |
| `inception.phases.{fase}.status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `completed` |

**Fases de inception (6 fases internas, secuenciales):**

| Fase | Key | Descripcion |
|------|-----|-------------|
| Fase 0 | `context` | Bienvenida y contexto del proyecto |
| Fase 1 | `discovery` | Product Brief, Stakeholders, Backlog, Riesgos, NFRs, KPIs, Tech Constraints |
| Fase 2 | `ddd` | Domain-Driven Design (Bounded Contexts, Entidades, VOs, Eventos, Reglas) |
| Fase 3 | `architecture` | Stack tecnologico, ADRs, C4, Patrones (via architect) |
| Fase 4 | `scaffold` | Estructura del proyecto + Walking Skeleton (via scaffold) |
| Fase 5 | `environments` | Ambientes Cloud + Quality Tooling |

Estas fases permiten retomar inception desde donde se quedo si la sesion se interrumpe.

### Feature

| Campo | Valores |
|-------|---------|
| `features[].status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `in_review`, `done`, `blocked` |
| `features[].phases.{fase}.status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `completed`, `blocked` |
| `features[].phases.{fase}.approved` | `true`, `false` |

### HU

| Campo | Valores |
|-------|---------|
| `userStories[].status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `in_review`, `done`, `blocked` |
| `userStories[].phases.{fase}.status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `completed`, `blocked` |
| `userStories[].phases.{fase}.approved` | `true`, `false` |
